product.name: White Wallpaper White Contact Paper Thicken Peel and Stick Wallpaper 24"x394" Matte Solid Textured Contact Paper Self Adhesive Removable Waterproof for Cabinets Furniture Bedroom Livingroom
product.description:
Slight texture gives it a painted look and hides slight imperfections.
Thick enough to be durable yet thin enough to take corners and flexible to work with.
Thick Material
Advanced PVC material, thickened without color transmission, more suitable for family use.
Waterproof
Waterproof design, while decorating your room, it is easier to clean, just wipe with a wet towel to restore a clean appearance.
Self-adhesive
Just peel and stick it off (please clean the wall before use to ensure that your wall has a flat, dry, and non rough surface).
Easy to cut
There is a size line on the back, according to the size you measure, cut along the size line to reduce waste.
product.bullet_points:
• PACKAGE CONCENTS--Color: Matte Peel and Stick, Solid White. 24" X 394"/Roll（In other words,1.97’x 32.8’/Roll ), it covers 64.6 sq.ft per roll.Comes with a plastic scraper and Installation instruction.
• Fashion appearance:Slight texture gives it a painted look and hides slight imperfections.The smooth surface layer of the wallpaper is mixed with looming texture, and the texture is whirling, extending the space.
• EASY USE:Self-adhesive. Just peel and stick. Removable without sticky residue.Applied to smooth surfaces, wall decoration,furniture renovation,can meet your different DIY needs.
• LARGER SIZE--This white textured wallpaper is 24 inch wide, there would be less seam in the surface than the narrow item.
• CUSTOMER SERVICE--If you have any questions (such as product size, color, etc.), please feel free to contact us. We are always committed to providing you with the best service.
